      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. MEPUNGA SPIRIT has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. Hit the frame latest (29.66) when second at Sandown in a Grade 6. Has the ability and should feature. 1. RADAR O'REILLY ran below his best last time finishing fourth (30.08) over 515m at Sandown in a Restricted WIN. Got the money at his only try from this box. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. 8. VICTORY ALBERT was out of the placings last time but recorded an impressive Mix 6/7 win (29.73) at Sandown three runs back. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. 5. JUNEAU PETE has claims fresh from a recent placing.\",\"runners\":[2,1,8,5],\"exclusive\":false}",
